comments: Barnes (SAC) makes marginal contact to Bates-Diop's (MIN) body on his driving shot attempt.
Okogie (MIN) makes contact to Fox's (SAC) body during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Hield (SAC) makes contact to McLaughlin's (MIN) arm/side during his drive but contact does not affect his SQBR.
Fox (SAC) places a resting hand to McLauglin's (MIN) front during his drive that does not affect his SQBR.
Hield (SAC) moves alongside of McLaughlin (MIN) with a collapsing arm against his side, contesting his driving shot attempt.
Bates-Diop (MIN) blocks the shot attempt by Bogdanovic (SAC) and makes incidental contact to his body after the blocked shot.
Barnes (SAC) establishes legal position in Martin's (MIN) path during the pick and makes slight contact as they disengage.
Bogdanovic (SAC) places his hand against Reid's (MIN) front when marginal contact is made on Reid's (MIN) play at the basket.
Reid (MIN) makes contact to Barnes' (SAC) arm during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Fox (SAC) commits a take foul on Okogie (MIN).
Bates-Diop (MIN) makes contact to Hield's  (SAC) arm that affects his ability to follow through on his shot.
Hield (SAC) commits a take foul on Napier (MIN).
Hield (SAC) makes marginal contact to Napier's (MIN) front as he disengages from the contact during the inbound.
Napier (MIN) avoids making contact to Hield's (SAC) arm during his shooting motion on the jump shot attempt.
Towns (MIN) establishes legal position in Barnes' (SAC) path during the pick and absorbs the contact.
Wiggins (MIN) commits a take foul on Fox (SAC).
Fox (SAC) enters the lane prior to the shot hitting the rim.
Towns (MIN) makes  marginal contact to Fox's (SAC) body during his shooting motion that does not affect his play at the basket.
Bazemore (SAC) briefly grasps Towns' (MIN) arm and separates without affecting his FOM.
Bazemore (SAC) makes slight contact with Towns (MIN) off ball that does not affect his ability to get to the pass.
Bazemore (SAC) places a resting hand against Towns' (MIN) back that does not affect his trajectory on his jump shot attempt.
Bogdanovic (SAC) establishes himself in a screening position in Towns (MIN) path and absorbs the contact.
Towns (MIN) makes contact to Fox's (SAC) wrist during his shooting motion that affects his jump shot attempt.
Towns (MIN) establishes himself in a legal screening in Barnes' (SAC) path during the screen.
Covington (MIN) places a hand/arm to Fox's (SAC) front during the drive but contact does not affect his SQBR.
As Okogie (MIN) reaches across Hield's (SAC) body he makes incidental contact with his shoulder/chest.
Napier (MIN) avoids making contact to Bogdanovic's (SAC) arm during his shooting motion on the jump shot attempt.
After Barnes (SAC) absorbs the contact during the screen by Towns (MIN) he places his hand momentarily to Towns side and slides it off.
Barnes (SAC) makes marginal contact with Wiggins' (MIN) body during his driving shot attempt.
Covington (MIN) extends his arm against Bjelica's (SAC) back and dislodges him from his position.
Towns (MIN) establishes legal position in Barnes' (SAC) path and absorbs the contact.
Okogie (MIN) draws Bazemore (SAC) into the air towards him and the contact affects his play at the basket.
Towns (MIN) makes incidental foot to foot contact with Barnes' (SAC) as they engage during the loose ball.
Bazemore (SAC) makes contact to Okogie's (MIN) arm during his shooting motion that affects his play at the basket.
Bjelica (SAC) makes a slight brush to Okogie's (MIN) front when the marginal contact occurs on the play at the basket.
Dedmon (SAC) makes some contact with Okogie (MIN) during the rebound but contact does not affect his ability to retrieve the ball.
Dedmon (SAC) legally gathers the ball as he falls to the floor.
Covington (MIN) briefly engages with Bjelica (SAC) and separates during the pick.
Towns (MIN) establishes himself in a screening position in Bogdanovic's (SAC) path and makes slight contact as they disengage.
Wiggins (MIN) steps out of bounds on the sideline prior to his pass.
Covington (MIN) moves laterally into Fox's (SAC) path during his drive and contact affects his SQBR.
Napier (MIN) commits a take foul on Bazemore (SAC).
